('Bulbule Lake', 'bulbule-lake', 'Lake', 'Karnali Province', 'Small spring-fed lake near Jumla. Local name means "bubbles" from fresh springs.', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1439066615861-d1e4672a254d?w=800&q=80', 4.3, 8, 2700, 'Easy', ARRAY['Jan', 'Feb', 'Mar', 'Apr', 'May', 'Jun', 'Jul', 'Aug', 'Sep', 'Oct', 'Nov', 'Dec'], false),
